    seoDescription: `Explore the sacred Bagmati River as it flows through Sarlahi District in Nepal's Madhesh Province. Learn about Chhath Puja pilgrimages, the Kabilasi Temple, wetland ecology, and how to visit this holy Terai waterway.`,
