    bookingCity: `Kathmandu`,
    seoTitle: `Kapilvastu Nepal | Ancient Kingdom of the Buddha's Early Life`,
    seoDescription: `Visit Kapilvastu and the Tilaurakot archaeological site — the ancient Shakya kingdom where Siddhartha Gautama spent his first 29 years. A key stop on Nepal's Buddhist pilgrimage circuit in Lumbini Province.`,
