    seoDescription: `Visit Devdaha in Rupandehi, Nepal — the ancient homeland of Queen Maya Devi, mother of the Buddha. A sacred Buddhist site near Lumbini connected to the origins of Buddhism. Guide to history, location, and visiting.`,
