    seoDescription: `Climb Shreenagar Hill above Tansen in Palpa, Nepal, for breathtaking views of Dhaulagiri, Annapurna, and Machhapuchhre. Discover this hidden western Nepal viewpoint above the medieval town of Tansen.`,
    published: true,
